                                                    to complete the upgrade process within 2 working days to:</p>
                                                <!-- UPGRADE END -->
                                                <%} else {%>
                                                    <!-- REGISTRATION -->
                                                    <p>Kindly request you to courier/hand deliver a payment of Rs. 2,500/- (+GST)
                                                        to complete the registration process within 2 working days to:</p>
                                                    <!-- REGISTRATION END-->
                                                    <%}%>
                                                        <%}%>
                                                            <!-- TEXT TO BE CHANGED AS PER THE UPGRADE/REGISTRATION END-->


                                                            <!-- COMMON TEXT -->
                                                            <p class="sfa-bold">6th Floor, 17A, Raviraj House, Saraswati Road, Off Linking Road,
                                                                Santacruz (W), Mumbai 400054</p>

                                                            <p>Failure to make the payment will result in
                                                                <span class="sfa-bold">CANCELLATION </span> of your entry.</p>

                                                            <p>
                                                                <span class="sfa-bold">Kindly Note:</span> Registrations for SFA Championship 2018-19,
                                                                City Name is 2 STEP Process. You will be able to access Sports
                                                                Registration (STEP 2) via your SFA ID & password on successful
                                                                verification. </p>

                                                            <p>For further queries kindly call us on 7045684365/66/67. </p>
                                                            <!-- COMMON TEXT END -->

                                                            <!-- REGARDS -->
                                                            <p style="font-family:TitilliumWeb-Bold; font-weight: bold;">Regards,
                                                                <br>Team SFA</p>
                                                            <!-- REGARDS END -->
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>
